{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_da4b0b53c02d447d8716cc33","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t<!-- GitHub Markdown Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/writing-on-github/getting-started-with-writing-and-formatting-on-github -->\n2\t\n3\t<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mampfes/hacs_waste_collection_schedule/master/images/icon.png\" alt=\"Waste Collection Schedule logo\" title=\"Waste Collection Schedule\" align=\"right\" height=\"60\" />\n4\t\n5\t# Waste Collection Schedule\n6\t\n7\t**A custom component for Home Assistant that retrieves waste collection schedules from a wide range of service providers.**\n8\t\n9\t<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mampfes/hacs_waste_collection_schedule/master/images/wcs_animated.gif\" alt=\"Waste Collection Schedule animation\" title=\"Waste Collection Schedule\" align=\"right\" height=\"200\" />\n10\t\n11\tWaste collection schedules from service provider web sites are updated daily, derived from local ICS/iCal files, or generated from user-specified dates or regularly repeating date patterns. The Home Assistant built-in Calendar is automatically populated with schedules, and there is a high degree of flexibility in how information can be format and displayed in entity cards or pop-ups. The framework can easily be extended to support additional waste collection service providers, or other services which provide schedules.\n12\t\n13\t# Supported Service Providers\n14\t\n15\tWaste collection schedules in the following formats and countries are supported. Click on the section heading to view details of individual service providers.\n16\t\n17\tIf your service provider is not listed, feel free to open a [source request issue](https://github.com/mampfes/hacs_waste_collection_schedule/issues/new?assignees=&labels=source+request&projects=&template=SOURCE-REQUEST.yml&title=%5BSource+Request%5D%3A+) (please first check the [Issues section](https://github.com/mampfes/hacs_waste_collection_schedule/issues) if there already is an open issue for your service provider.).\n18\t\n19\t<details>\n20\t<summary>ICS/iCal and User-Specified</summary>\n21\t\n22\t- [Generic ICS / iCal File](/doc/source/ics.md)\n23\t- [User Specified](/doc/source/static.md)\n24\t- [Multiple Sources Wrapper](/doc/source/multiple.md)\n25\t\n26\t</details>\n27\t\n28\t<!--Begin of country section-->\n29\t<details>\n30\t<summary>Australia</summary>\n31\t\n32\t- [1Coast - Central Coast](/doc/source/1coast_com_au.md) / 1coast.com.au\n33\t- [Adelaide Hills Council](/doc/source/app_my_local_services_au.md) / ahc.sa.gov.au\n34\t- [Adelaide Plains Council](/doc/source/app_my_local_services_au.md) / apc.sa.gov.au\n35\t- [Alexandrina Council](/doc/source/app_my_local_services_au.md) / alexandrina.sa.gov.au\n36\t- [Alexandrina Council](/doc/source/frwa_com_au.md) / alexandrina.sa.gov.au\n37\t- [App Backend of My Local Services](/doc/source/app_my_local_services_au.md) / localcouncils.sa.gov.au\n38\t- [Armadale (Western Australia)](/doc/source/armadale_wa_gov_au.md) / armadale.wa.gov.au\n39\t- [Australian Capital Territory (ACT)](/doc/source/act_gov_au.md) / cityservices.act.gov.au/recycling-and-waste\n40\t- [Banyule City Council](/doc/source/banyule_vic_gov_au.md) / banyule.vic.gov.au\n41\t- [Baw Baw Shire Council](/doc/source/impactapps_com_au.md) / bawbawshire.vic.gov.au\n42\t- [Bayside Council](/doc/source/impactapps_com_au.md) / bayside.nsw.gov.au\n43\t- [Bayside Council (Victoria)](/doc/source/bayside_vic_gov_au.md) / bayside.vic.gov.au\n44\t- [Bega Valley Shire Council](/doc/source/impactapps_com_au.md) / begavalley.nsw.gov.au\n45\t- [Belmont City Council](/doc/source/belmont_wa_gov_au.md) / belmont.wa.gov.au\n46\t- [Benalla Rural City Council](/doc/source/impactapps_com_au.md) / benalla.vic.gov.au\n47\t- [Berri Barmera Council](/doc/source/app_my_local_services_au.md) / berribarmera.sa.gov.au\n48\t- [Blacktown City Council (NSW)](/doc/source/blacktown_nsw_gov_au.md) / 